  "text": "Blockchain is a technology that is set to change how we currently conduct business in any given sector. Blockchain, in conventional terms, is a public ledger that records all events, transactions and exchanges that happen between parties or nodes in the network [CITATION_1] . Bitcoin popularized the concept of blockchain, but blockchain as a baseline platform has far greater implications than bitcoin itself.",
